VALUES
    ('Street Fighter Alpha 3', 'Engage in fierce one-on-one battles in Street Fighter Alpha 3. Choose from a roster of iconic fighters, each with unique abilities and special moves. With fast-paced gameplay and stunning visuals, this classic fighting game delivers an arcade experience like no other.', 'Fighting', 'PlayStation 1', 5, 1999, 14.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/91439-street-fighter-alpha-3-playstation-front-cover.jpg'),
