    ('Metal Gear Solid', 'Step into the world of tactical espionage in Metal Gear Solid. As Solid Snake, you infiltrate a nuclear weapons facility to neutralize a terrorist threat. With cinematic storytelling, complex characters, and innovative gameplay mechanics, Metal Gear Solid redefined the stealth genre.', 'Stealth', 'PlayStation 1', 5, 1998, 29.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/8618053-metal-gear-solid-playstation-front-cover.jpg'),
