    ('Grand Theft Auto V', 'Explore the vast open-world of Los Santos in Grand Theft Auto V. Play as three distinct protagonists and engage in heists, missions, and mayhem. With stunning visuals, a dynamic narrative, and a living, breathing game world, GTA V sets a new standard for open-world games.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 3', 7, 2013, 39.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/6090098-grand-theft-auto-v-playstation-3-front-cover.jpg'),
