    ('Battlefield 4', 'Engage in intense modern warfare in Battlefield 4. With a dynamic multiplayer experience and a gripping single-player campaign, Battlefield 4 showcases the chaos of large-scale battles. Utilize vehicles, teamwork, and strategy to emerge victorious on the battlefield.', 'First-Person Shooter', 'PlayStation 3', 7, 2013, 24.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/6731533-battlefield-4-playstation-3-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('God Of War (2018)', 'Experience the reimagined journey of Kratos and Atreus in God of War (2018). This action-adventure masterpiece takes you through the realms of Norse mythology, featuring epic battles, a gripping narrative, and stunning visuals. With a powerful father-son dynamic, God of War (2018) sets a new standard for storytelling in gaming.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 4', 8, 2018, 49.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/8019897-god-of-war-playstation-4-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('Red Dead Redemption II', 'Immerse yourself in the vast landscapes of the American Wild West in Red Dead Redemption II. As Arthur Morgan, navigate the challenges of the Van der Linde gang and experience a narrative-rich open-world adventure. With stunning realism, deep character development, and a dynamic ecosystem, RDR2 is a true western epic.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 4', 8, 2018, 59.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/7422709-red-dead-redemption-ii-playstation-4-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('Bloodborne', 'Descend into the nightmarish world of Yharnam in Bloodborne. This action RPG challenges players with fast-paced combat, eldritch horrors, and intricate level design. With its gothic atmosphere and relentless difficulty, Bloodborne captivates players seeking a dark and challenging gaming experience.', 'Action RPG', 'PlayStation 4', 8, 2015, 39.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/11078336-bloodborne-playstation-4-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('Sekiro', 'Master the way of the shinobi in Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice. From the developers of Dark Souls and Bloodborne, Sekiro offers intense swordplay, stealth, and a captivating feudal Japan setting. With precision combat and a focus on mastery, Sekiro provides a unique and challenging experience for players.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 4', 8, 2019, 54.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/7868291-sekiro-shadows-die-twice-playstation-4-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('Doom Eternal', 'Unleash hell on Earth in Doom Eternal. This fast-paced first-person shooter puts players in the boots of the Doom Slayer as they face hordes of demons. With relentless action, dynamic weapons, and visceral combat, Doom Eternal continues the legacy of the iconic Doom series.', 'First-Person Shooter', 'PlayStation 4', 8, 2020, 44.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/8654561-doom-eternal-playstation-4-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('Black', 'Embark on an adrenaline-fueled journey through the shadows of covert operations in Black. As an elite operative, you navigate through intense urban environments, engaging in high-stakes gunfights and explosive scenarios. With cutting-edge graphics and a gripping narrative, Black delivers an immersive experience that blurs the line between chaos and precision.', 'First-Person Shooter', 'PlayStation 2', 6, 2006, 19.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/4359409-black-playstation-2-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas', 'Explore the sprawling landscapes of San Andreas, a fictional state teeming with criminal opportunities. In Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas, you step into the shoes of Carl Johnson as he returns to his hometown to confront corruption, betrayal, and chaos. This open-world masterpiece allows players to engage in a gripping narrative, diverse missions, and an expansive range of criminal activities.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 2', 6, 2004, 29.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/4554918-grand-theft-auto-san-andreas-playstation-2-front-cover.jpg'),
    ('God Of War II', 'Ascend the heights of Mount Olympus once again as Kratos, the God of War, in this epic sequel. God Of War II thrusts players into a world of Greek mythology, combining intense combat, intricate puzzles, and a gripping storyline. With improved graphics and an evolved combat system, Kratos seeks revenge against the gods in a quest that challenges both his strength and his humanity.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 2', 6, 2007, 39.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/5088103-god-of-war-ii-playstation-2-front-cover.jpg'),
