    ('Shadow of the Colossus', 'Embark on a hauntingly beautiful quest in Shadow of the Colossus, a unique blend of action and exploration. As Wander, you traverse a desolate landscape on horseback, seeking to resurrect a loved one. The games innovative approach features colossal, majestic creatures as the only adversaries, each requiring careful strategy and skillful climbing. Shadow of the Colossus captivates with its emotional narrative and breathtaking environments.', 'Action-Adventure', 'PlayStation 2', 6, 2005, 34.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/4317156-shadow-of-the-colossus-playstation-2-front-cover.jpg');
